 comparable, there are subtle morphological\ndifferences between galaxies in these different classes, and that the\ncentrally-quenched galaxies formed their stars systematically earlier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Dec 2022 16:46:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2023 14:18:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
