etrically\nthin AD, the recovered time-delay spectrum is consistent with black hole masses\nderived with 30% uncertainty.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Dec 2022 20:37:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 12:57:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
